{"type": "article", "id": 9169, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-05-05T07:45:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 9661, "name": "饼桌"}, {"id": 2976, "name": "灯饰"}, {"id": 3704, "name": "鞋子"}, {"id": 2523, "name": "服饰"}, {"id": 811, "name": "家居"}, {"id": 22, "name": "环保"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 9662, "name": "Polit"}], "category": 17, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605215906h3e2kTgt7j5B1DOa.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tTimes 4 Coffee Table by Gonçalo Campos\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tGonçalo Campos 最近为法国新兴品牌 Polit 推出了一款“饼桌”。一个圆桌被切开了四分之一，桌子的内部有四个色彩不同的颜色分区，方便用户区分不同的存储用途，当桌面静止时，桌子看起来像极了一个表格中的饼图，因此得名。这是<a href=\"http://www.goncalocampos.com/\" target=\"_blank\">工作室的官方主页</a>，可以查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215851YHoQMD53IWqesghX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.540625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215852jtZEdTh87yMVmonC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052158527uknedsUFxJO3Xp8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80416667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215853nXg2RU16CzrQmiSq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75416667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tBalakuxe Pendant Light by Ben Wahrlich\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t最近，新西兰设计师 Ben Wahrlich 为 Anaesthetic 设计了一款名为“星座”的灯饰产品，这款产品由两个到六个 Bala 吊灯组成，也就是星座中的“星星”，整个系列有六种不同排列方式，适合不同的房间选择。比如，双子座由简单的两个灯组成，而双鱼座由六盏灯组合而成。材料上使用的是抛光黄铜，更增加了星空的闪烁感。这是 <a href=\"http://anaestheticdesign.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Anaesthetic 的官方主页</a>，可以看到他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215854IObx14yHCs0zBavJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58924205\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052158543NqiLUrjRTelhg5u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060521585540nxLipg7M8f9IUv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215855B6I27iQUr3OJHsb8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215855gjQmeOMNtvnT375R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tZero Energy Furniture by Raphaël Ménard &amp; Jean-Sébastien Lagrange\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t设计师 Raphaël Ménard 和 Jean-Sébastien Lagrange 共同设计了一款零耗能的桌子。其工作原理是在桌子的实木表面和下部阳极氧化铝之间放置了一层相变材料，吸收过剩热量并存储热量，用作后期的供热。这个桌子是 Z.E.F.（零能耗家具）项目的第一个阶段作品，这个项目的目的在于，在提供轻巧优雅的家具的同时，最大化气候调控和家用能源的效能。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215856Yrw5lbeSxWnT4DtC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215857rmLMKv1zWP2lh5Ag.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69791667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215857MSQkqxnHfs0yRip1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215858BF4itcQaRWdDlTLZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t WOAWWESRT by Midwest Vintage &amp; Woaw\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t香港最著名的美式复古服饰专卖 Midwest Vintage 与潮流生活店 Woaw 联手推出了一个牛仔拼布系列，包括 T 恤，无袖夹克、短裤、钮扣衬衫等男女装服饰，以及电脑包，围裙等生活方式单品。他们从美国西部服饰汲取灵感，使用拼接面料，将丹宁元素融入设计之中。目前该系列计划在 5 月 7 日至 28 日于 WOAW Store “WOAWWEST” 主题 Pop-up 期间限定店铺发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215858mnRbxD7Sfj4erTaY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215859IKJdvM4OD3k0sLHw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215859y2VTj8P6MXIYqxsW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215859cTomAR26vuMWKLsH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215900kVR8JvczUM4hQy0m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052159006tOI0dbzDxjlFkVc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215901PnSAOKRjrDpICHWu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215901WFfdl2HVmogExCIz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215902sftvS27A0893mnjZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215902eBwV4H0huL6c1vI7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tZenji by Nike\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tNike 最近推出了新的 Zenji 系列鞋款，这款鞋子以 Nike 此前备受欢迎的 Roshe Run 为设计灵感，整个系列以黑色为主色调，与 Roshe Run 同样，保持一致的流线型鞋底和黑网状鞋面。其透气性和舒适性强，是炎热夏季里面运动搭配的一个可以考虑的选择。这是<a href=\"http://store.nike.com/us/en_us/pd/zenji-shoe/pid-10267975/pgid-10267976\" target=\"_blank\">官方网站购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215902BWgLONoP1EFbv3Vh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215903yvinY1tBLmN6Rro5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215903aBGXmNL5Yxi230Ed.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215904iyTx78K2hQtnlZeI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052159046bIiXkNrAWmVnvaq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}